Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
04 May 2010	cnwjk3	Initial creation

*/

vars

begin
	// The drawing frame should be set to resize with its parent. We just need to make sure that we also resize the TI frame...
	self.resizeDrawingFrames();
	self.refresh();
epilog

end;</source>
